@startuml
!pragma teoz true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam DefaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam DefaultFontSize 13
title 图3  ENCORE 票务管理系统 网络拓扑

cloud "互联网 / 内网" as Net

node "用户终端" {
  [游客 / 注册用户\nWeb 浏览器] as UserPC
  [票务管理员\nWeb 浏览器] as AdminPC
  [检票员\nWeb 浏览器 / 平板] as CheckPC
}

node "Web 服务器\n(Nginx 80/443)" as Nginx
node "应用服务器\n(Spring Boot 8080)" as App
database "数据库服务器\n(MySQL 8 / 3306)" as DB
database "缓存服务器\n(Redis / 6379)" as Cache

UserPC --> Net
AdminPC --> Net
CheckPC --> Net
Net --> Nginx : HTTPS
Nginx --> App : HTTP/JSON + WebSocket(/ws) (内网)
App --> DB : JDBC (内网)
App --> Cache : RESP (内网)

note bottom of Nginx
  外网入口仅暴露 80/443
  其余端口在内网通信
  WebSocket(/ws) 经 Nginx Upgrade 透传
end note
@enduml
